# Include Directory

This project currently keeps public firmware headers inside
`lib/Luefterklappe/src` so PlatformIO can build the library as a self-contained
module. Add files here only for project-wide headers that are shared outside a
specific library.

Rules:

- Keep MCU-independent interfaces in `lib/Luefterklappe/src`.
- Keep Pico/Arduino-specific declarations near `src/main.cpp` or a future HAL
  adapter.
- Do not put generated headers, build artifacts or local SDK files in this
  directory.
